Package: snyk
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ca-certificates, libc6
Description: Snyk CLI security scanner and MCP server
 The Snyk CLI scans and monitors your projects for security vulnerabilities
 across open-source dependencies, container images, infrastructure as code,
 and first-party code.
 .
 This package ships the official Snyk standalone CLI binary, which also
 exposes a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server via "snyk mcp" for use by
 AI assistants and agentic workflows.
